    A seed protected by a adamantium shell fell through space. It hit an at=
mosphere and started to desend. Finally reaching the ground the adamantium =
shell was gone, melted off. All that was left was the seed.
    It grew at =
a rapid rate. Once it was completed it was a full grown, organic Base. (Loc=
ated in the most unlikely of places, Australia) It was a giant plant. From =
inside a pod grew, this pod contained an organic computer, within that comp=
uter was DNA and RNA. Creating a Emissary for the Organic it scanned (For l=
ack of a better word) the planet for the most dominate life form. It found =
Transformers. Using there abilities it created the leader Emissary. It pick=
ed the form of a life not seen on Earth he encorporated a beast mode into t=
he bot.
    Emissary stood, looking at his new home. He could feel his hear=
t pound in his chest. His Beast Mode is like the creature from The Relic. H=
is "robot" (Humaniod) mode is a Yautja (Predator/Predator 2) Without the ar=
mour.
